bodies; varying list of 75, 84, and 100 are
given.



[216]

<xa>朱</xa>Red, vermilion.

<xa>朱利</xa>caura, a thief, robber.

<xa>朱利草</xa>caurī, robber-grass or herb, name of a plant.
<pb n="220"/>

<xa>朱羅波梨迦羅</xa>Defined as 雜碑衣, i. e. cīvara, or ragged clothes.

<xa>次</xa>Second, secondary; a turn, next.

<xa>次第</xa>In turn, one after another.

<xa>次第緣</xa>無間緣 Connected
or consequent causes; continuous conditional or accessory

cause.

<xa>此</xa>This, here.

<xa>此世</xa>此生 This world,
or life.

