<xa>此岸</xa>This shore, the present life.

<pb n="221"/>
<xa>死</xa>marana; 末刺諵; mrta 母陀; to die, death; dead; also cyuti.

<xa>死亡</xa>Dead and gone (or lost).

<xa>死刀</xa>The (sharp) sword of death.

<xa>死山</xa>The hill of death.

<xa>死屍</xa>'Dead corpse, 'e. g. a wicked monk.

<xa>死海</xa>The sea of mortality.

<xa>死王</xa>Yama, 焰魔 as lord of death and hell.

