bridgehead for the expansion and

control of the outposts of the Chinese
empire in Central Asia.

<xa>咸</xa>All, entirely.

<xa>咸同</xa>All together.

<xa>品</xa>varga, 跋渠 class, series, rank, character; a chapter of a sutra.

<xa>上中下品</xa>Superior, middle, and lower class, grade, or rank.

<pb n="676"/>
<xa>垢</xa>mala. Dust, impurity, dregs; moral impurity; mental impurity.
Whatever

