nature.

<xa>姞</xa>Chi, name of the concubine of Huang Ti; translit. g .

<xa>姞栗陀羅矩吒</xa>(姞栗陀) grdhra, a vulture; Grdhrakūta, the Vulture Peak, v. 者.

