<pb n="684"/>

<xa>賢祥甁</xa>or 吉祥甁) vase of virtue, or of worth, or of good fortune.

<xa>帝網</xa>(帝釋網) ? Indra-jala. The net of Indra, hanging in Indra's 宮 hall, out of
which

all things can be produced; also the name
