<xa>乾陀訶提</xa>Gandhahastin, 'fragrant elephant, ' name of a Bodhisattva.

<xa>停</xa>To stop, rest, settle, delay.

<xa>停心</xa>To fix or settle the mind in meditation, cf. 五停心觀.

<xa>偶</xa>An image; a mate; unexpectedly.

<xa>偶像</xa>An image, an idol.

偸 [偷] Remiss; to steal; stealthy.

偸婆 stūpa, cf. 塔.

