called兜羅綿 (or 兜羅M016820); also a tree producing such floss.

<xa>減</xa>减 Diminish,
decrease, abate, reduce, abbreviate; opp. 增.

<xa>減劫</xa>The decreasing kalpas in which the period of life is gradually
reduced, as

the 增減 are the kalpas of increase; together they form twenty kalpas, ten

diminishing and ten increasing; but there
<pb n="936"/>
are other definitions.

<xa>減費</xa>To cut down one's personal expenditure (for the sake of charity).

