<xa>小參</xa>a special meeting; a discussion following an address.

<xa>參前</xa>Before the evening assembly.

<pb n="938"/>
<xa>參後</xa>參退 after the
evening assembly.

<xa>參問</xa>To seek instruction— generally as a class.

<xa>參堂</xa>The initiation to the services of one newly ordained.

<xa>參禪</xa>To inquire, discuss, seek religious instruction.

<xa>參詣</xa>To approach the gods or Buddhas in worship.

<xa>參請</xa>To request instruction, or discussion.

<xa>參頭</xa>One versed in the ceremonies and capable of leading others.

啓 To open, begin, inform.

啓白 idem 表白 To inform, make clear, especially to inform the Buddhas.

