<xa>商</xa>To consult arrange; trade, a merchant; translit. śan, sam,
śa, śā.

<xa>商佉</xa>商迦 śavkha,
<xa>餉佉</xa>(or 傷佉, 勝佉, 儴佉, ?佉, 霜佉) ; 勝伽; 企羅; 償起羅 A conch,
shell.

<xa>商羯羅</xa>Śavkara, 'auspicious' (M. W. ), a name for 'Śiva', and intp. as 骨鏁

bone-chains; name of 商羯羅阿闍梨 Śavkaracarya,
