a title of every Buddha; also 莎迦陀 (or 莎伽陀); 沙伽陀 (or 沙竭陀); 裟婆羯多; 蘇揭多.

<xa>沙羅樹</xa>The Sala-tree.

<xa>沙髻</xa>A crown of grass put on the head of 不動尊 q.v. as a servant of the
