<pb n="53"/>

practices, ceremonies, asceticism, etc.

<xa>處</xa>To dwell, abide; fix, decide, punish; a place, state. āyatana, 阿耶怛那, also tr.


<xa>入</xa>, place or entrance of the sense, both the organ and the sensation,
