<xa>蛇足</xa>Snake's legs, i.e. the nonexistent.

<xa>術</xa>Way or method; art; trick, plan.

<xa>術婆迦</xa>Śubhakara, a fisherman who was burnt up by his own sexual love.

<xa>被</xa>A quilt, coverlet; to cover; to suffer; sign of the passive.

<xa>被位</xa>Covered seats for meditation.

<xa>被葉衣觀音</xa>Guanyin clad in leaves.

<xa>袈裟</xa>kasāya, the monk's robe, or cassock. The word is intp. as decayed,
