v. 二十五條. A dyed
robe 'of a colour
<pb n="55"/>

composed of red and yellow' (M. W. ); it
has a number of poetic names, e. g.

robe of patience, or endurance. Also 迦沙曳 (迦邏沙曳).



[364]

<xa>袍</xa>a robe.

<xa>袍休羅蘭</xa>Bahularatna, Prabhūtaratna, abundance of precious things, the 多寳 Buddha of

