<xa>袍裳</xa>袍服 Upper and
lower garments.

<xa>許</xa>Grant, permit, admit, promise; very.

<xa>許可</xa>Grant, permit, admit.

<xa>設</xa>To set up, establish, institute; arrange, spread; suppose;
translit. ś.

<xa>設利</xa>(設利羅) śarīra, relics, remains, see 舍.

