<xa>設施</xa>Śacī, Śakti, v. 舍.

<xa>設覩嚕</xa>Śatru, an enemy, a destroyer, the enemy, also 設咄嚕; 設都嚧; 捨覩嚧 (or 轢覩嚧); 窣覩喚;

<xa>婆訥嚕</xa>.

<xa>設賞迦</xa>Śaśāvka. 'A king of Karnasuvarna, who tried to destroy the sacred

