<pb n="59"/>
from

appearing.

<xa>貪毒</xa>The poison of desire.

<xa>貪水</xa>Desire is like water carrying things along.

<xa>貪濁</xa>The contamination of desire.

<xa>貪煩惱</xa>The kleśa, temptation or passion of desire.

<xa>貪狼</xa>Greedy wolf, wolfish desire or cupidity.

<xa>貪瞋痴</xa>rāgadvesamoha, the three poisons.

<xa>貪結</xa>The bond of desire, binding in the chain of transmigration.

<xa>貪縛</xa>The tie of desire.

<xa>貪習</xa>The habit of desire, desire become habitual.

