position; a student.

<xa>導</xa>To lead, indicate, educe, induce.

<xa>導化</xa>To lead and convert, or transform.

<xa>導引</xa>To lead.

<xa>導師</xa>nāyaka; a leader, guide, one who guides men to Buddha's teaching;
applied

also to Buddhas and bodhisattvas, and to
the leaders of the ritual in Buddhist

services; v. 天人道師.

<pb n="521"/>
<xa>廨</xa>An official building; a monastic granary; 廨院主 the head
