<xa>燈滅</xa>The extinction of a lamp.

<xa>燈火</xa>dīpapradīpa, lamp-light.

<xa>燈籠</xa>燈爐 A lantern.

<xa>燄</xa>Flame, blaze; idem 焰; 爓 q.v.

<pb n="530"/>
<xa>燄口</xa>UIkā-mukha. Flaming mouth, a hungry ghost or preta, that is
