<xa>獨柯多</xa>v. 突 duskrta, offence.

<xa>獨生獨死獨去獨來</xa>Alone we are born and die, go and come.

<xa>獨空</xa>The one immaterial reality behind all phenomena.

<pb n="531"/>
<xa>獨股杵</xa>獨鈷 (獨鈷杵) The
