<xa>縛薩怛羅</xa>vastra, cloth, clothes.

<xa>縛迦</xa>vākya, speech, saying, sentence, word.

<xa>縛野吠</xa>Vāyavī, the deva of the north-west, v. Vāyu 縛臾.

