<xa>闇心</xa>A dark, ignorant, or doubting mind.

<xa>闇林</xa>Tāmasavana, see 答 10.

<xa>闇鈍</xa>Ignorant and dull.

<xa>闇障</xa>The hindrance of ignorance.

<xa>闍</xa>Translit. c, j, k, g, sounds.

<xa>闍世</xa>cf. 阿 Ajātaśatru.

<xa>闍伊那</xa>Jaina, the Jains, founded by Jñātrputra, cf. 若,
