<xa>闍那崛多</xa>Jñānagupta, a native of Gandhāra, tr. forty-three works into
Chinese A.D.

561-592.

<xa>闍那耶舍</xa>Jñānayaśas, a native of Magadha, teacher of Yaśogupta and
