co-translator of six works, A.D. 564-572.
<pb n="615"/>

<xa>闍陀伽</xa>idem 闍多伽 jātaka.

<xa>闍鼻多</xa>jhāpita, idem 荼毘.

<xa>隱</xa>To hide, conceal; obscure, esoteric; retired.

<xa>隱密</xa>Esoteric meaning in contrast with 顯了 exoteric, or plain meaning.

<xa>隱形</xa>隱身To vanish,
become invisible.

<xa>隱所</xa>A privy.

<xa>隱覆</xa>To hide, conceal; secret.

<xa>隸</xa>To control; retainers.

<xa>隸車</xa>v. 離.



[464]

<xa>鞠</xa>To nourish, exhaust, address; a ball; translit. ku, gu.

