<xa>豐</xa>Abundant.

<xa>豐財</xa>Wealthy.



[469]

<xa>轉</xa>vartana; pravartana; vrtti. Turn, transform, revolve,
evolve, change, the

process of birth and rebirth; again, re-.

<xa>轉世</xa>To return to this life.

