<xa>歡</xa>nanda. Pleased, glad.

<xa>歡喜</xa>Pleased, glad; pleasure, gladness.

<xa>歡喜丸</xa>(or 歡喜團, 喜團) Joy-buns, a name for a kind of honey-cake.

<xa>歡喜光佛</xa>Buddha of joyful light, Amitābha.

<xa>歡喜國</xa>妙喜國 Abhirati,
the happy land, or paradise of Aksobhya, east of our universe.

<xa>歡喜苑</xa>歡樂園; 喜林苑
